{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_ceylon_set_1", "eventName": "真心的禮物", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "真心的禮物", "storyInfo": "耶誕節前夕，錫蘭在商業街碰到了自己的同學琳茲。錫蘭盛情邀請對方陪自己挑選禮物，卻絲毫沒有注意到琳茲神色中的尷尬。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_school", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“幾個月前我剛進入大學的時候，寄了一張國立大學圖書館的明信片給你。”"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“那時我仰望著四周向穹頂延伸的書架，聽著走道上同學們的腳步聲在龐大的建築內迴響，我是多麼興奮啊。”"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我覺得這裡的知識是無窮的，其中一定有我要的答案——能治好你的方法。”"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“但現在站在同樣的地方，我總是感到一陣眩暈，走向書架的每一步也變得更加艱難。”"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我開始害怕圖書館、實驗室和教室，畏懼像過去一樣拼命努力；我在每一行看不懂的文字面前感到疲倦無比。”"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我忍不住想，要是我的時間不夠學習所有我想要的知識呢？”"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“......要是我就像抽乾汐斯塔的海一樣，窮盡了這裡的知識，卻仍然得不到那個答案呢？”"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我該怎麼辦？”"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——一張作廢的信箋，被折成三折塞在了垃圾桶底部。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "fadetime": 3.0, "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t“......聖誕節特款薩米風味肉桂熱飲，老少咸宜，家庭套餐買二送一，可抽取聖誕信使的驚喜玩具......”", "name": "商店廣播"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t“......冰原信使系列新款上架，給您家的溫暖......”", "name": "商店廣播"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t原來聖誕促銷活動已經開始了呀......每年這個時候商業區都會熱鬧起來。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t這家“賈桂琳小姐”茶室，自從黑回去之後我好像就沒來過了。對不起哦，賈桂琳小姐，你們的點心架份量太足了，我一個人吃不完。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t蘿茜百貨大樓應該就在轉角，不過黑已經陪我去逛過很多次了，大概沒有什麼可以讓她感到驚喜的禮物吧。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t那邊應該可以直接雇傭國際信使。雖說隊伍比別的地方長太多了，但是在商店街買好賀卡之後可以直接跟信一起寄出去。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t嗯，寄給父親的賀卡就不需要寫字了吧。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 250.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t啊，琳茲！中午好！", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "jump", "xpos": 10.0, "power": 5.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t欸、欸？中午好，錫蘭，沒想到會在這裡遇見你......", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t（小聲）怎麼是她啊，麻煩......", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t怎麼了？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t不，我沒說什麼......只是沒想到錫蘭你居然記得我的名字。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t咦，我看起來記憶力有那麼不好嗎？我記得剛開學的時候，就是你教會我怎麼區分維多利亞鑄幣的。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t除了走廊上的老式投幣售貨機和公用電話機，我從沒見過還有什麼地方用得上它們。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t自動售貨機接受的是老式鑄幣，但是我投進去的是新式鑄幣，所以它卡住了，還是靠你拍了半天才好。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t還有第一次“星期四詩與茶會”的時候，也是你事先提醒了我不要念威廉姆斯的詩，因為他太有名了。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t唉，文學畢竟不是我的興趣方向嘛！", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t那你估計也還記得上次野外考察的時候，你一個人的報告太詳盡，導致全組其他人貢獻度大大降低，獲得的分數也很難看。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t嗯？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t沒什麼，我是說，我也不是真的在懷疑你的記憶力。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你也是來逛街的嗎？", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t對呀，聖誕節要到了，該準備一些禮物了。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t正好，琳茲你是本地人，請你陪我逛逛可以嗎？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t雖說我也來維多利亞幾年了，但平時只會去大型百貨商店，對那些藏在街巷中的精品店還是不太瞭解。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t呃，我......", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t抱歉，你有別的事情要忙？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t對了，確實聖誕節假期前還有幾篇階段性報告要寫，你要是沒有心思逛街我也可以理解。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t不不，那些報告我已經完成一半了。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t拜託，會提前做功課的人也不是只有你一個。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t可是一旦做起實驗來，時間永遠是不夠的嘛。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t唉......", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你要買什麼樣的禮物？既然你那麼不想浪費時間，我們就動作快點。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t隨便看看也沒關係，我要準備的禮物有很多件呢。偶然看到中意的就買下來，這樣才算是逛街嘛。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t啊？......呃，沒想到你也會有隨便逛逛的閒心。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t只是今天覺得自己特別需要休息。正好，聖誕節也是個不錯的藉口。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t......你可真擅長讓人沒心情過節。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t算了，這邊的台階下去，巷子裡有一家手工巧克力店，我們先去看看吧。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t這家有二十幾種不重樣的禮盒，可以買來送給不同的人。這樣你應該能快點買完所有禮物吧。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G7_decisivebattlealley_d", "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 10.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 2.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "jump", "xpos": 0.0, "power": 3.0, "times": 5.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "jump", "xpos": 0.0, "power": 3.0, "times": 5.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t錫蘭，你有在聽我說話嗎？你又在想什麼啊？", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t啊，抱歉......", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你今天看起來可真奇怪。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t兩位女士，要嘗嘗我們這邊的聖誕新款嗎？店內有不同樣式的禮盒裝售賣哦。", "name": "店員"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t謝謝，我們正好要看巧克力，請多多介紹。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t嗯......這個試吃的巧克力味道不錯！請問這是哪一款？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t覆盆子碎配白巧克力，現在有雪景主題的聖誕禮盒款哦。", "name": "店員"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t琳茲你看！包裝感覺和薇薇安的髮色很搭呢，就送這個給她吧。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t嗯......嗯？", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t——你剛剛說要給薇薇安買禮物？", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t是哦，你是覺得巧克力太普通了嗎？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t不是，我是想，可是你們前兩天還吵了一架欸。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t唔，你指的是前兩天我們在理論課上討論狄安娜教授核心理念的事？那個我昨天已經向她道歉了呀。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t《源石、分離機與搖撼的大地》這本小冊子裡面，狄安娜教授對源石的應用實驗已經轉向民用範疇，但是之前我沒來得及讀到。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t不，也不僅是前兩天......每次小組合作開會的時候你們都在吵架吧？", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你們就像仇家一樣。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t有嗎？可是我覺得自己在她的幫助下獲得了很多新知識哦，感激她都來不及。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t個人的認知總是非常有限的，要接近真知，就必須要去找和自己想法不同的人，多多進行這樣的交流。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你啊......", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我會離開家鄉來到維多利亞學習，這應該是主要原因吧。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t在汐斯塔，人人都說感染者是無法被治癒的，所以我決定離開汐斯塔，看看其他地域、其他時代的人們會不會有不一樣的回答。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t古老的維多利亞，會不會比年輕的汐斯塔懂得更多呢？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t大概會吧......", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t——欸，等等，感染者？錫蘭你是想治療感染者？", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t嗯，你是不是覺得這個想法不太......", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t難怪你會莫名其妙地申請選修藥學院的課程，還直接把陳述書投到了學院院長的信箱裡，鬧出了不小的動靜。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t不過國立大學的藥學院可是出了名的嚴格，就算他們接受一個旁聽生，大概也不會給你任何資質證明吧。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t給不給資質證明倒是沒關係，只是我......", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#11$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t——啊，店員小姐，您好，請幫我挑兩盒禮盒裝巧克力一起結帳吧，謝謝。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t好的，請來這邊。", "name": "店員"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_032", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t唉，結果完全沒找到機會把她趕走，差點還聽她講下去了。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t要不我現在自己溜走吧。再這麼一直陪著她，我今天來商業街要做的事情就做不成了。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我買好了，接下來我們去哪裡？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t......你回來得可真及時。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t對了，因為琳茲你今天在場，所以今天我不會買你的聖誕禮物，只會買其他朋友的禮物。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t呃，還有我的聖誕禮物？我們的關係有那麼......", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t（小聲）唉，你要是知道我做了什麼，肯定就不會覺得我是你的朋友了。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t畢竟當著你的面買的話，就不算驚喜了嘛。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t咳......咳咳！啊，是呢，是這樣的。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t好啦，拜託你帶路啦，我們去下一家看看吧。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t嗯......雖然最重要的一件禮物還沒有挑好，不過今天選不到也沒關係。畢竟“最重要”的東西，不多花點心思可不行。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t除此之外要買的就只剩下一張賀卡了。買完之後去那邊辦理一下國際信使雇傭服務，今天的任務就算結束了。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t又要寄國際郵件？你的家書也太頻繁了吧......雇傭費可不便宜。而且，你不是馬上就要回家了嗎？", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我還要過好多天才能到家呢。再說，這張賀卡，寄回去比當面遞交好。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t說起來，琳茲你自己還什麼都沒買，是不是我耽誤你的計畫了？你要是有什麼想去逛逛的店鋪，也可以帶著我一起去嘛。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t天都快黑了，再晚一點店鋪可都要關門了。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t......唉，好吧，我認命了。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我想去那邊的家居用品店看看，你要是沒有興趣的話不用等我。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t家居用品嗎？我很有興趣！", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t（小聲）......我還是比較希望你沒有興趣。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_032", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slbellbtl"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t您好，我是琳茲，昨天在你們店裡下過預購單，這是取貨碼。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t啊對了，麻煩直接包裝好可以嗎？是送人的禮物。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 3.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t沒問題。核驗完畢，這是您預訂的商品。需要繫上聖誕卡片嗎？", "name": "店員"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_032"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t不，不用了，謝謝。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你買了什麼？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t全自動茶壺，按照說明書放入定量的水和茶包，它就會幫你控制水溫，保證你泡出來的紅茶口感。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我聽說過！唔，不知道是用怎樣的源石施術單元實現的呢......能不能拆開看看說明書......", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t咳，這個你拿著繼續研究吧，不用還給我了。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t咦？這不是你送人的禮物嗎？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t......呃。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t它是送給你的。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$holiday_intro", "key": "$holiday_loop", "volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你想笑就笑吧。我也沒想到這麼不巧。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t噗。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t之後同學們一起喝下午茶的時候，如果你願意用這個茶壺而不是自己手工沏茶，我會非常高興的......其他人估計也會很高興。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t謝謝你。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t可是現在離聖誕節還有一個月，離我們放假也還有兩周欸。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t（深呼吸）", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t這不是聖誕禮物，是我向你表示歉意的禮物。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t欸？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t......請不要那麼茫然地看著我，你這樣會讓我更加沒勇氣認錯的。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t對不起，我以前一直不敢跟你講話。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t呃，其實不僅是我，大家都有點害怕你。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t嗯？為什麼會害怕我啊......因為我想治療感染者？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "jump", "xpos": 0.0, "power": 6.0, "times": 2.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t不是，完全不是！我之前都沒聽說過這件事！我只是覺得你實在太努力了！", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t一個來自炎熱城市的人能在冬季的早上六點爬出被窩去圖書館佔位子，到底是多可怕的自律能力啊！", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t早上十點去吃早午餐的時候碰到你捧著書在迴廊上踱步，感覺你打招呼的眼神都像是在說“怎麼這個時間才起床”一樣。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t總之，錫蘭你就像冷冰冰的鏡子一樣，我走過的時候就會看到自己懶惰散漫的樣子。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我有那麼冷冰冰的嗎？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t別、別誤會，我是在誇你。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t——對了，我想冒昧地問一個問題可以嗎？", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你有關係很好的感染者朋友嗎？", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t哎？！", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t......嗯，有哦。她是我最重要的人。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t她現在還好嗎？", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t情況一直很穩定。沒有什麼東西能打倒她，礦石病也不能。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t那就好。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t......還有，她不在維多利亞，所以這裡的管理條例對她不生效，如果你想對她......", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t不不，我沒有惡意，也不是什麼獵奇的心態。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我們可是源石研究者欸，也許哪天因為實驗事故、觀測時的突發狀況，甚至因為自己主動的意願，我們都可能感染礦石病。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我們知道它是什麼，或者至少比大多數人更接近於知道。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t......謝謝你，琳茲。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t唉，也許應該是我來說感謝吧。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t就像你的理想是治療感染者一樣......來國立大學讀書，選擇了源石研究這個專業的人，就算是我，也有自己小小的理想。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我雖然知道學者的理想就意味著實現前人未能達成的事情，意味著要把一條路走到頭，然後自己開闢出新的道路......但我遠沒有做好準備。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t前人未能達成的事情......", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t——還好有你這樣的榜樣在身邊。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t是這樣嗎？我......有能力成為這樣的人嗎？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#11$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#11$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我真的是在誇你呀，別露出那樣的表情。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t不，別在意。我剛剛是想起了別的事情......想通了一些事情。", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t對了，我要把這件禮物還給你。之前只是我們還不熟悉而已，這有什麼可道歉的？", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t啊......那個，最重要的事情我還沒說呢......", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t其實我要道歉的是，因為不敢跟你說話，所以我也沒有告訴你，之前天災現場採集的源石樣本出現了一些稀有反應。", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t什麼！", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_348_ceylon_1#7$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我對自己的實驗方法和觀測結果都沒有什麼信心，總覺得只是我自己少見多怪......", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t......要是錫蘭你看了之後說這不是什麼新發現，我該有多丟臉呀！", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t所以，即使我知道你應該是對這些進展最有興趣的人，我也沒敢分享——", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 250.0, "fadetime": 1.7, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.8, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 20.0, "fadetime": 0.8, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我們快跑起來！下一班回學校的車還有三分鐘到站！", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 170.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 170.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t只要趕在實驗室關門之前溜進去，我們就可以在裡面待一晚上！", "name": "錫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_348_ceylon_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_032"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 170.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 170.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t呃，那個好像是違反規定的吧......慢、慢點跑，我手臂要被你拽脫臼啦！", "name": "琳茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_032"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 5.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.8, "crossfade": 1.5}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_340_shwaz_2#2", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t老爺，小姐來信了。", "name": "黑"}, "figure_art": "char_340_shwaz_2#2"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_024"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t嗯？你都要動身去接她回來了，這封信來得可真夠晚的。", "name": "赫爾曼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_024"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我猜，那丫頭一如既往地沒在信裡提到我。", "name": "赫爾曼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_024"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_340_shwaz_2"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t......", "name": "黑"}, "figure_art": "char_340_shwaz_2"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑的視線下意識地又一次掃過她已經記住內容的信件。"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“......入冬之後的圖書館裡似乎有一種靠源石技藝維持的暖爐，坐在裡面讀書非常愜意。我這個學期的借閱書單已經很長很長了。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "middle", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“......隨著和同學熟悉起來，我也得到了很多幫助。以前我尋求治療礦石病的方法時，並沒有想得太深入，但現在這些困惑已經化解了。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“是的，我現在知道要如何破解礦石病的奧秘了。相信我，我很快就要找到它啦。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“......隨信附上一張賀卡，幫我轉交給父親吧。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "取出這遝信紙之後的信封是空的，國際信使的發信郵戳證明這封信在落款之後三天才寄出。"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_340_shwaz_2#1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t（小姐一定又被什麼東西迷住，把信的事情全忘記了吧。）", "name": "黑"}, "figure_art": "char_340_shwaz_2#1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_340_shwaz_2#5"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t不，老爺。小姐在信裡特地祝您聖誕快樂，她很期待聖誕夜的餐桌。", "name": "黑"}, "figure_art": "char_340_shwaz_2#5"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}